者であり、梶がうららのフィアンセであることを承知でセックスに励んでいると言う。\r\nいやらしい笑みを浮かべる莉子は、残酷な事実を淡々とうららに語り掛けるのだった。\r\n\r\nゆっくりとプレイングルームの中へと歩いていくうらら。\r\nセックスの最中だった梶と明日香もうららに気付き、その異様な佇まいに驚き軽く悲鳴を上げると腰を抜かしてしまう。\r\n壁際まで追い詰められたふたりを前に、不気味な笑顔を浮かべるうらら。\r\n完全に狂った状態のうららが、ふたりにつぶやく。\r\n「ビ……リーブ……」","date":"2013-06-28","images":null,"rating":{"rank":4780,"total":568,"score":6.6,"count":{"1":7,"2":7,"3":9,"4":26,"5":67,"6":154,"7":158,"8":83,"9":28,"10":29}},"tags":[{"name":"里番","count":462},{"name":"鈴木みら乃","count":210},{"name":"实用","count":107},{"name":"凌辱","count":87},{"name":"NTR","count":83},{"name":"2013","count":72},{"name":"百合","count":60},{"name":"18X","count":58},{"name":"RIN×SEN＋Ran→Sem","count":55},{"name":"OVA","count":48},{"name":"白浊","count":35}],"eps":2,"collection":{"wish":508,"collect":1099,"doing":50,"on_hold":87,"dropped":65}},{"id":78967,"type":2,"name":"开心超人","name_cn":"开心超人","summary":"在科技发达的星星球上，宅博士率领五个超人保护星星球的安全。\r\n一天，开心超人与怪兽搏斗中意外打断了网络电缆，造成星星球网络混乱，谁知这是灰心星球大大怪将军的计划。幕后的邪恶怪物（变形怪）通过入侵网络控制了星星球，后果一发不可收拾！市中心突然出现一座神秘建筑物，蓝光防御系统轻易被破，五超人的机车严重损毁，超人身受重伤……星星球只剩下脆弱的市民们，受伤的开心超人将如何保卫家园呢？","date":"2013-06-28","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/7b/dc/78967_UmLH6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/7b/dc/78967_UmLH6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/7b/dc/78967_UmLH6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/7b/dc/78967_UmLH6.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/7b/dc/78967_UmLH6.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":6490,"total":210,"score":6.1,"count":{"1":3,"2":0,"3":4,"4":6,"5":43,"6":92,"7":37,"8":13,"9":4,"10":8}},"tags":[{"name":"国产","count":62},{"name":"剧场版","count":48},{"name":"2013","count":32},{"name":"童年","count":31},{"name":"原创","count":30},{"name":"开心超人","count":16},{"name":"战斗","count":13},{"name":"TV","count":8},{"name":"动画电影","count":7},{"name":"2010s","count":6},{"name":"国漫","count":6}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":14,"collect":535,"doing":5,"on_hold":5,"dropped":20}},{"id":79973,"type":2,"name":"Mickey Mouse Season 1","name_cn":"米老鼠2013 第一季","summary":"Mickey Mouse is an American series of animated shorts created by Disney Television Animation. It features classic cartoon characters Mickey Mouse, Minnie Mouse, Donald Duck, Daisy Duck, Goofy Goof, and Pluto Pup in contemporary settings such as Paris and New York. The series will have the slapstick feel of classic Mickey Mouse shorts, as well as place the titular character in humorous situations that showcase his pluck and rascality, along with his long-beloved charm and good hearted-ness. It is being executive produced and directed by Emmy Award-winning artist Paul Rudish, known for his work on the Cartoon Network series Dexter's Laboratory and The Powerpuff Girls. It was announced at Disney's upfront meeting on March 12, 2013 for a premiere on June 28 on Disney Channel, with a total of 19 episodes, the first of which was made available on Disney's website as a \"special preview\".","date":"2013-06-28","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/0a/d5/79973_6nkk6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/0a/d5/79973_6nkk6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/0a/d5/79973_6nkk6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/0a/d5/79973_6nkk6.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/0a/d5/79973_6nkk6.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":1992,"total":78,"score":7.2,"count":{"1":2,"2":2,"3":0,"4":1,"5":3,"6":8,"7":22,"8":29,"9":8,"10":3}},"tags":[{"name":"TV","count":20},{"name":"欧美","count":16},{"name":"迪斯尼","count":13},{"name":"米老鼠","count":12},{"name":"童年","count":10},{"name":"2013","count":9},{"name":"泡面番","count":9},{"name":"迪士尼","count":4},{"name":"原创","count":4},{"name":"无节操","count":4},{"name":"美国","count":3}],"eps":18,"collection":{"wish":21,"collect":131,"doing":17,"on_hold":9,"dropped":15}},{"id":439615,"type":2,"name":"Foxed!","name_cn":"狐·变","summary":"　　Emily has been Foxed! This stop-motion tale is about fighting for what's right. Director James Stewart crafts a cautionary adventure about growing 